{"word":"H2940 - טַעַם - ṭaʻam - tah'-am - Advice","slug":"H2940","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">טַעַם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ṭaʻam"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tah'-am"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Advice"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D8;&#x05E2;&#x05DD; - t&#x0323;a&#x201B;am</b> - <i>tah'-am</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H2938\">H2938</a>; properly a <i>taste</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>perception</i>; by implication <i>intelligence</i>; transitively a <i>mandate: - </i>advice, behaviour, decree, discretion, judgment, reason, taste, understanding."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2938\">H2938</a>, <a href=\"#/H4303\">H4303</a>"}]}